《'''孖展風雲'''》（{{lang-en|''Margin Call''}}）是一部於[[2011年電影|2011年]]上映的美國[[獨立電影|獨立電影]]，[[J·C·陈多尔|J·C·陈多尔]]编剧并执导，[[凱文·史貝西|凱文·史貝西]]、[[黛咪·摩爾|黛咪·摩爾]]、[[保羅·貝特尼|保羅·貝特尼]]、[[傑瑞米·艾恩斯|傑瑞米·艾恩斯]]、[[柴克瑞·恩杜|柴克瑞·恩杜]]、[[史丹利·圖奇|史丹利·圖奇]]、[[西蒙·貝克|西蒙·貝克]]和[[潘·巴奇利|潘·巴奇利]]主演。内容讲述一家[[投资银行|投资银行]]36小时所发生的事情（以[[雷曼兄弟|雷曼兄弟]]破产<ref name="GUARDIAN01252011">Kay, Jeremy, [http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/filmblog/2011/jan/25/margin-call-sundance-review "Margin Call is a fine crash movie, but no banker"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/filmblog/2011/jan/25/margin-call-sundance-review |date=20130115052014 }}, ''The Guardian'' (UK), Tuesday 25 January 2011</ref><ref>Grynbaum, Michael M., [http://www.nytimes.com/2011/10/16/movies/margin-call-from-j-c-chandor-looks-at-wall-street.html?hpw "Wall Street, With Calm, Not Hysteria"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/10/16/movies/margin-call-from-j-c-chandor-looks-at-wall-street.html?hpw |date=20190104072826 }}, ''The New York Times'', October 12, 2011</ref>和[[2007-2008年环球金融危机|2007-2008年环球金融危机]]為主題）<ref name="Dash">{{cite news |first=Eric |last=Dash |title=Citi Goes Hollywood for Spacey and Crew |newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |date=2010-06-22 |url=http://dealbook.blogs.nytimes.com/2010/06/22/citi-goes-hollywood-for-spacey-and-crew/ |accessdate=2010-06-27 |archive-date=2010-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100829133105/http://dealbook.blogs.nytimes.com/2010/06/22/citi-goes-hollywood-for-spacey-and-crew/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |first=Mike |last=Fleming |work=Deadline New York |title=''Margin Call'' Director J.C. Chandor Snags Big Warner Bros Writing Gig From DiCaprio |url=http://www.deadline.com/2010/09/margin-call-director-jc-chandor-gets-big-warner-bros-writing-gig/ |date=2010-09-13 |accessdate=2010-10-06 |archive-date=2013-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131017160159/http://www.deadline.com/2010/09/margin-call-director-jc-chandor-gets-big-warner-bros-writing-gig/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |first=Borys |last=Kit |title=Simon Baker, Paul Bettany eye indie drama |magazine=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=2010-06-15 |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/news/e3i7acb6b7c0df1eb709c8bcff91327b23f |accessdate=2010-06-27 |archive-date=2010-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100623090732/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/news/e3i7acb6b7c0df1eb709c8bcff91327b23f |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

== 劇情 ==
紐約一家投資銀行的分析師發現公司財產評估有漏洞，使其面臨破產風險，這個驚人的發現使公司高層連夜召開會議，決定以低價拋售股票和債權，但此舉將會引起金融界的極-{}-大風-{}-暴。

