== 製作與發行 ==
主要拍攝於2010年6月21日在[[紐約市|紐約市]]開始<ref name="Dash"/>，而其中80%的場景皆在一家貿易公司的42樓攝影<ref>{{cite web |last=Wallace |first=Benjamin |url=http://nymag.com/movies/features/zachary-quinto-2011-10 |title=What’s Up, Spock?: He might be a famous Vulcan, but Zachary Quinto has no problem being fully human |work=New York Magazine |date=2011-10-16 |access-date=2016-11-24 |archive-date=2021-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125032206/https://nymag.com/movies/features/zachary-quinto-2011-10/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |first=Jon |last=Chesto |url=http://blogs.wickedlocal.com/massmarkets/2011/10/22/director-of-margin-call-didnt-need-a-big-budget-to-concisely-depict-wall-streets-mortgage-meltdown/ |title=Director of "Margin Call" didn’t need a big budget to depict Wall Street's mortgage meltdown |work=WickedLocal.com |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111025235930/http://blogs.wickedlocal.com/massmarkets/2011/10/22/director-of-margin-call-didnt-need-a-big-budget-to-concisely-depict-wall-streets-mortgage-meltdown/ |archivedate=2011-10-25 |access-date=2016-11-24 }}</ref>。電影的首映於2011年[[日舞影展|日舞影展]]上舉行，之後也有在{{link-en|第61屆柏林電影節|61st Berlin International Film Festival}}上展出，並獲[[金熊獎|金熊獎]]提名<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.berlinale.de/en/archiv/jahresarchive/2011/08_pressemitteilungen_2011/08_pressemitteilungen_2011detail_8532.html |title=The Competition of the 61st Berlinale |accessdate=2011-01-20 |work=Berlinale |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304203946/http://www.berlinale.de/en/archiv/jahresarchive/2011/08_pressemitteilungen_2011/08_pressemitteilungen_2011detail_8532.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vindianz.com/entertainment/spacey-moore-and-3d-in-focus-at-berlin-film-fest-afp-203000.html |title=Spacey, Moore and 3D in focus at Berlin film fest |accessdate=2011-01-20 |work=Yahoo News |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131113015739/http://www.vindianz.com/entertainment/s