== 反響 ==

=== 評價 ===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度88%，基於網站收集的155條評論，平均分為7.3/10<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/margin_call/ |title=Margin Call |work=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2012-01-10 |archive-date=2015-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151110113954/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/margin_call/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上，根據38篇影評，平均分獲得76分（滿分100）<ref name="metacritic">{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/margin-call |title=Margin Call |publisher=[[CBS|CBS]] |work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=2011-11-10 |archive-date=2020-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024065319/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/margin-call |dead-url=no }}</ref>，收穫普遍好評。《[[紐約客|紐約客]]》影評人{{link-en|大衛·登比|David Denby}}表示該片為「有史以來最好的[[華爾街|華爾街]]題材電影。」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newyorker.com/arts/critics/cinema/2011/10/31/111031crci_cinema_denby?currentPage=1|title=All That Glitters|work=[[The_New_Yorker|The New Yorker]]|accessdate=2016-11-26|archive-date=2013-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131113021041/http://www.newyorker.com/arts/critics/cinema/2011/10/31/111031crci_cinema_denby?currentPage=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>

